  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The &apos;Foster Family&apos; program of Instituto Fazendo Historia offers care and a home from volunteer families for children who are up to 3 years old, that need to be separated from their families for judicial reasons for a temporary or permanent amount of time.  The volunteer families take care of the child in their homes for a period of time that is transitional until the child returns to their family of origin or are adopted.   Our team selects, evaluates,trains and monitor the volunteer families.</narrative>
  </description>
